OL,3,CThree men guilty of plotting to murder
OL,4,C#54m Securitas robber
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police footage showing
OL,7,FDaniel Kelly and Louis Ahearne walking
OL,8,Fin Worcester Crescent just prior to
OL,9,Fthe shooting of Paul Allen in his home.
OL,11,FThree men from Woolwich have been
OL,12,Ffound guilty of plotting to kill a
OL,13,Fformer cagefighter convicted of
OL,14,FBritain's largest cash robbery.
OL,16,FPaul Allen, then 41, was paralysed for
OL,17,Flife after shots were fired at his
OL,18,Flarge detached rented home in Woodford
OL,19,FGreen, north-east London, in 2019.
