OL,3,CThree men guilty of plotting to murder
OL,4,C#54m Securitas robber
OL,6,FA jury at the Old Bailey was told the
OL,7,Fintention was to kill him, and the
OL,8,Fattackers "very nearly succeeded".
OL,10,FOn Monday, Louis Ahearne, 36, his
OL,11,Fbrother Stewart Ahearne, 46, and
OL,12,FDaniel Kelly, 46, were found guilty of
OL,13,Fplotting to murder Allen with others
OL,14,Funknown.
OL,16,FReacting to the verdicts in the dock,
OL,17,FStewart Ahearne shouted to the jury:
OL,18,F"You are only human. That's all I have
OL,19,Fto say about that."
