OL,3,CThree men guilty of plotting to murder
OL,4,C#54m Securitas robber
OL,6,FAllen was convicted at Woolwich Crown
OL,7,FCourt in 2009 for his part in
OL,8,FBritain's biggest armed robbery, at
OL,9,FSecuritas in Kent, in which #54
OL,10,Fmillion in cash was stolen, much of
OL,11,Fwhich has never been recovered, the
OL,12,Fcourt heard.
OL,14,FDuring the trial, prosecutors alleged
OL,15,Fthe background to the shooting was
OL,16,Fthat Allen was a "sophisticated"
OL,17,Fcareer criminal. Securitas is a global
OL,18,Fsecurity services company specialising
OL,19,Fin intelligent protective services
OL,20,Fbuilt on people, technology and
OL,21,Fknowledge.
