OL,6,FIn 2019 Allen was released from prison
OL,7,Fand moved from south London to a large
OL,8,Fdetached property in Woodford, north-
OL,9,Feast London, where he lived with his
OL,10,Fpartner and young children.
OL,12,FThe court heard how the defendants had
OL,13,Fplanned the shooting carefully,
OL,14,Fcarried out surveillance and fitted a
OL,15,Ftracker device to the victim's car to
OL,16,Ftrack his movements.
