OL,3,CThree men guilty of plotting to murder
OL,4,C#54m Securitas robber
OL,6,FOn the night of the shooting, the
OL,7,Fthree defendants travelled from their
OL,8,Fhomes in southeast London to Woodford
OL,9,FGreen using a car that had been hired
OL,10,Ftwo days earlier by Stewart Ahearne.
OL,12,FWhile Stewart Ahearne waited in the
OL,13,Fcar, Kelly and Louis Ahearne snuck
OL,14,Finto a garden overlooking Mr Allen's
OL,15,Fback garden.
OL,17,FAt around 11.09pm, six shots were
OL,18,Ffired through the back doors and
OL,19,Fwindows, striking Mr Allen in the neck
OL,20,Fas he stood in the kitchen.
