OL,4,C#54m Securitas robber
OL,6,FThe men fled back to the waiting car,
OL,7,Fwhich drove away, leaving their victim
OL,8,Ffighting for his life.
OL,10,FDuring the police investigation, DNA
OL,11,Fwas recovered from the garden fence
OL,12,Fand matched Kelly and Louis Ahearne.
OL,14,FBullet casings in the garden were
OL,15,Fmatched to a Glock handgun that was
OL,16,Fcompatible with a laser sight
OL,17,Frecovered from Kelly's address.
