OL,6,FThe court also heard that the three
OL,7,Fmen snatched Ming dynasty antiques
OL,8,Fworth more than 3.5 million US dollars
OL,9,F(#2.78 million) from a Swiss museum
OL,10,Fshortly before the murder plot.
OL,12,FJurors heard agreed facts about the
OL,13,Fdefendants' "previous criminality"
OL,14,Frelating to a burglary at the Museum
OL,15,Fof Far Eastern Art in Geneva on June 1
OL,16,F2019, a month before Allen was shot.
OL,18,FThree pieces of Ming-era porcelain
OL,19,Fwere taken from the museum, which had
OL,20,Fa combined insurance value of
OL,21,F3,580,000 US dollars (#2,760,000).
