OL,6,FThe items were an early 15th century
OL,7,Fbottle with a secret pomegranate
OL,8,Fdecoration; a small wine cup known as
OL,9,Fthe "chicken cup"; and a 14th century
OL,10,FAn Huan phoenix design bowl.
OL,12,FThe defendants flew to Hong Kong on
OL,13,FJune 14 2019, where they attempted to
OL,14,Fsell the phoenix bowl at an auction
OL,15,Fhouse.
OL,17,FOn October 16 2020, Stewart Ahearne
OL,18,Fwas arrested with another man at a
OL,19,FLondon hotel as they tried to sell the
OL,20,FMing vase to an undercover police
OL,21,Fofficer.
