OL,6,FA later search of a property revealed
OL,7,Fa passport in the name of Stewart
OL,8,FAhearne and a book on Ming dynasty
OL,9,Fantiques, the court was told.
OL,11,FThe rental car hired by Stewart
OL,12,FAhearne from a dealership in Dartford,
OL,13,FKent, was used by the other two
OL,14,Fdefendants in a burglary on a gated
OL,15,Fcommunity in the county, the court was
OL,16,Ftold.
OL,18,FLouis Ahearne, from Greenwich, south-
OL,19,Feast London, and Stewart Ahearne and
OL,20,FKelly, both of no fixed address, had
OL,21,Fdenied the charge against them.
