OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Matt Webb who
OL,7,Fled the investigation said: "This
OL,8,Fattack may look like the plot to a
OL,9,FHollywood blockbuster but the reality
OL,10,Fis something quite different. This was
OL,11,Fhorrific criminality.
OL,13,F"The court heard how this was a clear
OL,14,Fand defined attempt to take a man's
OL,15,Flife with those responsible making
OL,16,Fsignificant efforts to ensure this was
OL,17,Fsuccessful.
